<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">Kia ora G=
rant, Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt of our letter. Fri=
day, 17 October after 2:</span><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;font-family:&q=
uot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:white">=E2=80=8A</span><span style=3D"font-=
size:1.0pt;color:white">00
 pm works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment co=
uld be scheduled accordingly. I also reserve my right to undertake</span><o:=
p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">&nbsp;</s=
pan><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Kia ora Grant,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt o=
f our letter.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Friday, 17 October after 2:00 pm works for me, and I=E2=
=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment could be scheduled according=
ly.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I also reserve my right to undertake independent test=
ing and assessment of the property to ensure a full and impartial evaluation=
.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Having reviewed the proposed plan, I=E2=80=99m concer=
ned the current testing schedule appears incomplete. It does not include the=
 first floor, roof cavity, or the large upper deck, and the basement coverag=
e seems partial, given the known extent
 of smoke, water, and chemical contamination.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I therefore request confirmation that the planned ins=
pection and sampling will be expanded to include all levels and relevant str=
uctural areas. Alternatively, please confirm that Tower will meet my reasona=
ble costs should I need to arrange
 independent specialists to carry out supplementary testing (including labor=
atory analysis).<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please confirm the final timing for the 17th and the r=
evised scope of testing once available.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Ng=C4=81 mihi,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Raffaella<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
